1 (b) Reuse or recycle at least 20% of such debris through methods other than
2 placement in a solid waste landfill by July 1, 2025 2027;
3 (c) Reuse or recycle at least 30% of such debris through methods other than
4 placement in a solid waste landfill by July 1, 2026 2028;
